己個學生做下愛咁，學生又諗下點屌個大波miss<br />\n再唔係就係最鍾意做愛果時拍下片，方便以後分手再要脅下個前度做多幾次分手愛<br />\n台妹最馨同條仔吵兩句嘴就馬上搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛<br />\n個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿<br />\n所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂"},{"pid":"b27f9886aa5e9c9f15bb762e12595fd34a701110","tid":918103,"uid":72735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"記得之前有單又係咁<br />\n但係告返轉頭，話個正室用錄音筆係非法偷錄私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3b6dfaf7af5291712f3bdcc0d4e4d72e8c34af","tid":918103,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"係咪施記者？"},{"pid":"355021a67fc40307edb38459cc86c215e5876237","tid":918103,"uid":30368,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"Check偈油姐"},{"pid":"4b6929a4524e7667cde42d324c8a2b275e41b425","tid":918103,"uid":53498,"like":160,"dislike":1,"score":159,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"台灣網民：<br />\n<br />\n兩人是在車內教導插花。花瓶到底了，因而濺出好多水。"},{"pid":"9883f1c430e015dfd08c60f05bee88e1ddaf387d","tid":918103,"uid":29846,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">事後對夫撤告</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到個男嘅好似冇責任，條女錯晒咁"},{"pid":"35a8719d91a89020ad43c61ec302917b95c153c7","tid":918103,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞成份都色情小說集咁"},{"pid":"f3a5008ce6c257fb20d812913df1dec35aa2daa6","tid":918103,"uid":156772,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"15060ef41f4bfab9b1690b0f010cdfcc72d132de","tid":918103,"uid":61492,"like":28,"dislike":7,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"小三40歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"rep